name: Wood labyrinth
description:
What is this game?

Have you ever played with a wood labyrinth? Do you remember how satisfied you where when you finally could do it without falling in those little holes? This is what I tried to make with this game!!! I have to admit some levels are really hard but i am sure you can do it!!!

What Kind of game is it?

Its a puzzle game and a dexterity game at the same time!!!

On what can i play it?

-Linux

-Windows

-Mac
